headline: Fidelity Real Estate Investment Portfolio Q4 2024 Fund Review
summary: For the fourth quarter of 2024, the U.S. real estate investment trust market returned -7.61%, significantly lagging the 2.41% gain of the broad U.S. stock market, according to S&P 500 index.
